# games/system-tests/battery.jsonl wins if present. Each line: a SystemBatteryTest
# {slug, goal, notes?, suite?, max_iters?, pass_criteria?}. Slugs must match the
# sets in system_tests.SUITE_TESTS (smoke / pacman / full). Genre-free: these
# exercise distinct INTERACTION CLASSES (plumbing, free movement, turn-based
# select, asset animation, grid-maze), not specific titles.
