{"slug": "smoke-asset-animation", "goal": "Build a game with a single character that has an idle pose and a walk pose, animated by cycling generated sprite frames with drawImage (not code-drawn shapes). Arrow keys move the character and switch it to the walk frames. Expose window.state. R restarts.", "suite": "smoke", "max_iters": 4, "notes": "Generated-asset + frame-cycling class: drawImage sprites, animation reads as motion.", "pass_criteria": {"canvas_present": true, "images_loaded": true, "input_moves": true}}
